text: Martin Ernst Fischer (February 12, 1884 - February 4, 1971) was an American gymnast. He competed in four events at the 1904 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1884 births Category:1971 deaths Category:American male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of the United States Category:Gymnasts at the 1904 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
